<h1 class=" size-s ">
<span itemprop="headline">This Is What Happens When Bitcoin Miners Take Over Your Town</span>
</h1>
<p class="subhead">
Eastern Washington had cheap power and tons of space. Then the suitcases of cash started arriving.</p>
</header>
